<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<script src="../js/jquery.js"></script>
<script src="../js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script src="../js/add.js"></script>
<script src="../js/layer.js"></script>
<link href="../css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<link href="../css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<link href="../css/add.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<link href="../css/layer.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<link href="../css/layer.ext.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<title>商品分类</title>

</head>
<body>

<div class="page-wrapper">
<div class="container-fluid">
	<ul class="breadcrumb">
		<li>您的位置</li>
		<li ><a href="#">商品</a></li>
		<li ><a href="#">添加商品</a></li>
		<li class="active">其他信息</li>
	</ul>
	<div class="btn-group btn-group-justified" role="group" aria-label="Justified button group">
	   <a href="添加商品.html" class="btn btn-info " role="button">基本信息</a>
	   <a href="详情描述.html" class="btn btn-info" role="button">SKU信息</a>
	   <a href="详情描述.html" class="btn btn-info" role="button">价格体系</a>
	   <a href="相关商品.html" class="btn btn-info" role="button">相关商品</a>
	   <a href="其他信息.html" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">其他信息</a>
    </div>
	<form class="form-horizontal media-control">
		<div class="panel panel-default">
			<div class="panel-heading">
				其他信息
			</div>
			<div class="panel-body">
				<div class="form-group">
					<label class="col-sm-2 control-label" >关键词</label>
					<div class="col-sm-5">
						<input type="text" class="form-control"  placeholder="多个关键词请用“空格”隔开">
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
						<label class="col-sm-2 control-label" >描述</label>
					<div class="col-sm-5">
						<textarea rows='10' class="form-control"></textarea>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
						<label class="col-sm-2 control-label" >后台备注：</label>
					<div class="col-sm-5">
						<textarea rows='10' class="form-control" placeholder="仅管理员可见"></textarea>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
					<label class="col-sm-2 control-label" >完成状态</label>
					<div class="col-sm-3">
						<select class="form-control" >
							<option>请选择完成状态</option>
							<option>完成</option>
							<option>待补充</option>
							<option>待修改</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div class="col-sm-7">
						<p style="margin-top:8px;">此商品的添加状态，是否需要补充或修正</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="form-group">
						<label class="col-sm-2 control-label" >商品展现形式：</label>
					<div class="col-sm-6">
						<p class="switch-control">
							<button class="btn btn-default btn-nocircle">显示</button>
							<button class="btn btn-primary btn-nocircle">关闭</button>
							<span> 展示形态默认合并形式，3层级及以上销售属性选择时建议展开形式。</span>
						</p>
						<div class="clearboth">
							<div class="color-title">颜色：</div>
							<div class="colorspan-wrapper">
								<span class="span-content"><i>主图</i>红色/170</span>
								<span class="span-content"><i>主图</i>红色/170/定制版</span>
								<span class="span-content"><i>主图</i>红色</span>
								<span class="span-content"><i>主图</i>蓝色</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="clearboth">
							<div class="color-title">尺寸：</div>
							<div class="colorspan-wrapper">
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
								<span class="span-content">120</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

	</form>
	</br>
		<div class="text-center">

			<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary " >保存</button>
			<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary " >保存后继续添加</button>
		</div>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
